on=\"😎\"> Lush forests, diverse wildlife.</li> \r\n                                  </ul>\r\n                              </div>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                          <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6\">\r\n                              <div class=\"jeep-grid\">\r\n                                  <img src=\"/newAssets/img/timing.png\" class=\"icons\">\r\n                                  <h4 class=\"cardheader text-center\">Timing</h4>\r\n                                  <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\n                                      <li data-icon=\"🦄\"> Safari: 6 AM-6 PM (	🐘:1 hr) </li>\r\n                                      <li data-icon=\"🦄\"> Pick Morning/Evening slots when booking.</li>\r\n                                      <li data-icon=\"🦄\"> Confirm timings with Elephant Safari Coordinator post-booking.</li>\r\n                                  </ul>\r\n                              </div>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>','<div class=\"safari-jim-corbett\" data-aos=\"fade-right\">\r\n      <div class=\"container safari\"> \r\n        <div class=\"section-title\">  \r\n              <h2>Safari in Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n            </div> \r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"safari-header-content\">\r\n                <div class=\"row\">\r\n                    <div class=\"noticeable-li\"><p><b>Note: </b>Dear Traveler, Forest Department has proposed for rate increase in safari, if the same gets approved, you will be required to pay the difference amount at the time of your safari.</p></div>      \r\n               <div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n                <div class=\"box1\">                    \r\n                    <h3>Jeep Safari Price &amp; Safari Zones</h3>\r\n                    <table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n                        <tbody>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td><strong>Price (Indian)</strong></td>\r\n                                <td>INR 7500 / - Jeep (Maximum 6 Persons &amp; 2 children (b/w - 5 to 12 years) are allowed in ONE Jeep)</td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td><strong>Price (Foreigner)</strong></td>\r\n                                <td>INR 16000 / Jeep (Maximum 6 Persons &amp; 2 children (b/w - 5 to 12 years) are allowed in ONE Jeep)</td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td><strong>Zones</strong></td>\r\n                                <td>Bijrani / Garjiya / Jhirna / Dhela / Durgadevi / Phato / Sitabani</td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td><strong>Timings</strong></td>\r\n                                <td>Morning 6:00 AM - 9:00 AM | Evening 1:30 PM - 5:00 PM (Safari Timing Varies as Season Changes)</td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td><strong>Inclusions</strong></td>\r\n                                <td>Permission of CTR, Jeep, Driver, Permit and All Entries &amp; Taxes.<br>\r\n                                    * Guide Fee to be paid by the guest on the spot directly.<br>\r\n                                    * Pick &amp; drop is not included from hotels.\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </tbody>\r\n                    </table>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n                <h3>Canter Safari Price &amp; Zone</h3>\r\n                <table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n                    <tbody>\r\n                        <tr>\r\n                            <td><strong>Price (Indian)</strong></td>\r\n                            <td>INR 2500 / Person (ONE Canter has 16 Seats)</td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                        <tr>\r\n                            <td><strong>Price (Foreigner)</strong></td>\r\n                            <td>INR 4500 / Person (ONE Canter has 16 Seats)</td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                        <tr>\r\n                            <td><strong>Zones</strong></td>\r\n                            <td>Peaceful Dhikala</td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                        <tr>\r\n                            <td><strong>Timings</strong></td>\r\n                            <td>Morning 6:00 AM - 11:30 AM | Evening 12:00 PM - 5:30 PM</td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                    </tbody>\r\n                </table>\r\n                <p class=\"ptext\">This is a place on the planet Earth where you can find an immense variety of stately Royal Bengal\r\n                    Tiger, a wide variety of flora and fauna dwelling in their natural habitats. It is advantageous for\r\n                    the tourist to visit the Jim Corbett park because it remains open throughout the year. For the\r\n                    convenience of tourists and streamlining tourism management Corbett Tiger Reserve has been divided\r\n                    into six mutually exclusive tourism zones, each having separate gate for entry.</p>   \r\n                \r\n            </div>      \r\n            </div>   \r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n      </div>\r\n  </div>','<div class=\"container booking-procedure\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-title\">\r\n        <h2>Advance Jim Corbett Safari Booking Procedure:</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n        <div class=\"row \">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                        <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The full name, age, sex of each visitor as printed the same on the identity cards to be\r\n                            provided along with the confirmatory amount for Jim Corbett national park safari booking\r\n                        </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Preferred traveling dates and Safari Timings</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Advance Safari entry fee</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Specific ID card number of the ID proof that you are holding which might be voter ID,\r\n                            Aaadhar No., Driving Licence No., etc.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>If a permit is booked through the electronic source, it is not refundable.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Carry with yourself the same ID card which you used during the booking</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Intimidate us for at least 30 days in advance.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Foreign tourist can book for about 90 days in advanced</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The passport details are mandatory for making the reservation of Foreign tourists</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Zone will be allowed as per availability, your safari will be conducted in any one Zone\r\n                        </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Dhikala Canter Safari only operates from 15th Nov to 15th June of every year. It is\r\n                            closed for the remaining time due to the rainy season..</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>','<div class=\"container booking-procedure mb-4\">\r\n    <div class=\"section-title\">\r\n        <h2>Information to be kept in mind for Corbett Safari Booking</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Tourists are requested to obtain the entry pass that was being issued during online\r\n                            booking for Jim Corbett safari.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The entry permit is provisional and can be canceled without any prior intimation.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The Director of Corbett Tiger Reserve is supreme authority and his decision will be final\r\n                            as all is being governed under him.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The entry permit is strictly not transferable.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The official registered guides can only join the excursion. Do not change them for mutual\r\n                            convenience.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>After Sunset, entry to National Park is strictly prohibited.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>On Saturday and Sunday price may be high.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Dhikala tourist Zone is not permitted for the tourist who did not stay in the forest\r\n                            lodge.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>Getting down from the vehicle while you do the jeep safari is strictly prohibited.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>No pets will be allowed inside the CTR so, avoid carrying them.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/newAssets/img/checklist.png\" class=\"iconslist\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>All visitors are expected to act responsibly following all the rules and regulations as\r\n                            given above. Do the needful with the cooperation.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>','<div class=\"container entry-procedure p-2\">\r\n    <div class=\"section-title\">\r\n        <h2>Entry Formalities</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n                <div class=\"info-list\">\r\n                    <div class=\"info-text\">\r\n                        <p>The Corbett National Park is one of its kind restricted area. It is highly being abode by\r\n                            all the rules and regulations which the tourist need to follow for the safe and secure\r\n                            visit. It will of mutual convenience as the safety of the tourists is our topmost\r\n                            priority. You need to take the approval of officials to visit the core areas of the\r\n                            target locale.</p>\r\n                        <p>There are two sets of authority permits that are issued by the government for the\r\n                            tourists going to Corbett Safari Zone. First is the day visit Permit and the second is\r\n                            the night stay permit issued by the government for the forest rest houses. Day visit\r\n                            permit is required to visit the Park in the daytime with a certain stipulated limit.\r\n                            Indian national tourist as well as foreign tourists, both are required to keep the day\r\n                            pass for going to any Area of Jim Corbett. The second is the night stay permit. This\r\n                            permit is important to ensure your accommodation at the Forest Lodge. Issue by the\r\n                            government authorized officials, this is something which will serve as a guarantee of\r\n                            stay. The minimum it can be booked is for 1 Night and the maximum it can be booked up\r\n                            till 3 Nights.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>        \r\n      </div>','','','','','',NULL,'2023-12-15 01:01:00'),(5,'dhikalabooking','safaribooking','safaribooking','Dhikala-LodgeBG.jpeg',NULL,'safaribooking','safaribooking','safaribooking','<section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"portfolio\">\r\n        <div class=\"image_container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"50\">\r\n  \r\n          <div class=\"section-title text-center\">\r\n            <h2>Our Gallery</h2>\r\n            <p>Immerse Yourself in Nature\'s Haven - Reserve Your Dhikala Adventure Today!</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n  \r\n            <div class=\"gallery_items\">\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/dhikala.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/2-large.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/5-large.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>              \r\n            </div>\r\n  \r\n            <div class=\"gallery_items \">\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/6-large.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/8-large.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>   \r\n            </div>\r\n  \r\n            <div class=\"gallery_items\">\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/Dhikala-Forest-Lodge.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/dhikala.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/dhikala-frh.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>  \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>','<div class=\"section-title\">\r\n                    <h2>Overview</h2>\r\n                  </div>  \r\n                    <div class=\"col-md-8 \">   \r\n                        <p>Dhikala Forest Lodge is one of the greatest accommodations facility provided at the helm of Dhikala Forest. It is a popular opinion that a wildlife trip in Uttarakhand is incomplete if you have not made a visit to this beautiful Lodge. The beauty around the lodge and the amazing wildlife experience of the forest is worth going on vacation here. Far away from the noise and pollution of city life, this is the trip which will facilitate in developing a deep connection with Nature. With thousands of variety of birds and animals, this is a dream spot of the photographers and they wish to assimilate each and every possible moment. The Royal Bengal Tiger, the elephant, Leopard, and cheetah are no less than any treat to watch. Only a few national parks give you the privilege to stay at the mid of them overnight and Corbett is one of them. Although it seems a bit fearful at the end, it will be the most exciting one ever.</p>\r\n                        <p>The Indians and the SAARC visitors have to book this place for about 46 days in advanced and the tourists from other foreign countries have to book this accommodation for about 91 days in advance. There are six different wings in the Dhikala Forest Lodge which can be categorized as follows:</p>\r\n                        <p>You will also find the accommodation facilities being available at Bijrani, Gairal, Jhirna, and Kanda Forest rest houses. The government is continuously making the efforts in order to increase the accommodation by adding annexes and dormitories. The Solar electric fences around the accommodation are strong enough to ensure your safe night at this place.</p>\r\n                    </div>','<section class=\"package_content\">\r\n      <div class=\"container mt-3\">\r\n        <div class=\"block\">\r\n          <div class=\"content\">\r\n            <p>Explore the beauty and wilderness of Jim Corbett National Park, often referred to as the <b>\'Land of Roar, Trumpet, and Song.\'</b> Nestled in the foothills of the Himalayas in Uttarakhand, India, this national park is a haven for nature enthusiasts and wildlife lovers. Covering a vast expanse, it offers a diverse range of flora and fauna in their natural habitats.</p>\r\n           \r\n            <div class=\"js-excerpt excerpt-hidden\" id=\"corbettContent\">\r\n              <h2>Key Info About Jim Corbett National Park</h2>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li>Home to the majestic Bengal Tiger</li>\r\n                    <li>Temperature ranges from 5°C to 30°C</li>\r\n                    <li>Famous for rich biodiversity and lush landscapes</li>\r\n                    <li>Must-have experiences: Jungle safaris, birdwatching, river rafting</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n      \r\n                  <h2>Types Of Accommodation Near Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n                  <p>Choose from a variety of accommodations to make your stay memorable:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li><strong>Resorts:</strong> Experience luxury in the heart of nature with resorts offering spa services and wildlife views.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Forest Lodges:</strong> Stay close to the wilderness in comfortable forest lodges with guided safari options.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Camps:</strong> For the adventurous, camping near Jim Corbett provides a unique and immersive experience.</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n  \r\n                  <h2>Dining &amp; Culinary Delights</h2>\r\n                  <p>Indulge in delicious dining experiences at Jim Corbett hotels, offering a variety of cuisines. Some properties feature on-site restaurants serving local and international dishes. Enjoy a taste of the region with specialties like:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li>Kumaoni Raita , Bhang Ki Khatai , Aloo Ke Gutke , Gahat Dal ,Madua Roti </li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n            \r\n                  <h2>Popular Areas To Explore Around Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n                  <p>Discover the beauty of the surrounding areas during your visit to Jim Corbett:</p>\r\n                  <p><strong>1. Dhikala:</strong> A popular area within the park known for its wildlife and birdwatching opportunities.</p>\r\n                  <p><strong>2. Ramnagar:</strong> The gateway to Jim Corbett, offering a blend of nature and cultural experiences.</p>\r\n                  <p><strong>3. Corbett Falls:</strong> A scenic waterfall where you can relax amidst lush surroundings.</p>\r\n             \r\n                  <h2>Activities &amp; Entertainment</h2>\r\n                  <p>Enhance your stay with various activities and entertainment options:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li><strong>Jungle Safaris:</strong> Explore the national park\'s diverse wildlife on guided safaris.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Adventure Sports:</strong> Engage in river rafting and other adventure activities for an adrenaline rush.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Local Markets:</strong> Visit nearby markets to buy local handicrafts, souvenirs, and traditional items.</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n            \r\n                  <h2>Getting Around In Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n                  <p>Discover the ease of transportation options in and around Jim Corbett:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li><strong>Jeep Safaris:</strong> Ideal for wildlife enthusiasts to explore the park\'s diverse terrain.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Taxis:</strong> Convenient for local travel, taxis offer flexibility in explorin