to\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>   \r\n            </div>\r\n  \r\n            <div class=\"gallery_items\">\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/Dhikala-Forest-Lodge.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/dhikala.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"/newAssets/img/dhikala-frh.jpg\" class=\"img-fluids\" alt=\"\"></div>  \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>','<div class=\"section-title\">\r\n                    <h2>Overview</h2>\r\n                  </div>  \r\n                    <div class=\"col-md-8 \">   \r\n                        <p>Dhikala Forest Lodge is one of the greatest accommodations facility provided at the helm of Dhikala Forest. It is a popular opinion that a wildlife trip in Uttarakhand is incomplete if you have not made a visit to this beautiful Lodge. The beauty around the lodge and the amazing wildlife experience of the forest is worth going on vacation here. Far away from the noise and pollution of city life, this is the trip which will facilitate in developing a deep connection with Nature. With thousands of variety of birds and animals, this is a dream spot of the photographers and they wish to assimilate each and every possible moment. The Royal Bengal Tiger, the elephant, Leopard, and cheetah are no less than any treat to watch. Only a few national parks give you the privilege to stay at the mid of them overnight and Corbett is one of them. Although it seems a bit fearful at the end, it will be the most exciting one ever.</p>\r\n                        <p>The Indians and the SAARC visitors have to book this place for about 46 days in advanced and the tourists from other foreign countries have to book this accommodation for about 91 days in advance. There are six different wings in the Dhikala Forest Lodge which can be categorized as follows:</p>\r\n                        <p>You will also find the accommodation facilities being available at Bijrani, Gairal, Jhirna, and Kanda Forest rest houses. The government is continuously making the efforts in order to increase the accommodation by adding annexes and dormitories. The Solar electric fences around the accommodation are strong enough to ensure your safe night at this place.</p>\r\n                    </div>','<section class=\"package_content\">\r\n      <div class=\"container mt-3\">\r\n        <div class=\"block\">\r\n          <div class=\"content\">\r\n            <p>Explore the beauty and wilderness of Jim Corbett National Park, often referred to as the <b>\'Land of Roar, Trumpet, and Song.\'</b> Nestled in the foothills of the Himalayas in Uttarakhand, India, this national park is a haven for nature enthusiasts and wildlife lovers. Covering a vast expanse, it offers a diverse range of flora and fauna in their natural habitats.</p>\r\n           \r\n            <div class=\"js-excerpt excerpt-hidden\" id=\"corbettContent\">\r\n              <h2>Key Info About Jim Corbett National Park</h2>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li>Home to the majestic Bengal Tiger</li>\r\n                    <li>Temperature ranges from 5°C to 30°C</li>\r\n                    <li>Famous for rich biodiversity and lush landscapes</li>\r\n                    <li>Must-have experiences: Jungle safaris, birdwatching, river rafting</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n      \r\n                  <h2>Types Of Accommodation Near Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n                  <p>Choose from a variety of accommodations to make your stay memorable:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li><strong>Resorts:</strong> Experience luxury in the heart of nature with resorts offering spa services and wildlife views.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Forest Lodges:</strong> Stay close to the wilderness in comfortable forest lodges with guided safari options.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Camps:</strong> For the adventurous, camping near Jim Corbett provides a unique and immersive experience.</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n  \r\n                  <h2>Dining &amp; Culinary Delights</h2>\r\n                  <p>Indulge in delicious dining experiences at Jim Corbett hotels, offering a variety of cuisines. Some properties feature on-site restaurants serving local and international dishes. Enjoy a taste of the region with specialties like:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li>Kumaoni Raita , Bhang Ki Khatai , Aloo Ke Gutke , Gahat Dal ,Madua Roti </li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n            \r\n                  <h2>Popular Areas To Explore Around Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n                  <p>Discover the beauty of the surrounding areas during your visit to Jim Corbett:</p>\r\n                  <p><strong>1. Dhikala:</strong> A popular area within the park known for its wildlife and birdwatching opportunities.</p>\r\n                  <p><strong>2. Ramnagar:</strong> The gateway to Jim Corbett, offering a blend of nature and cultural experiences.</p>\r\n                  <p><strong>3. Corbett Falls:</strong> A scenic waterfall where you can relax amidst lush surroundings.</p>\r\n             \r\n                  <h2>Activities &amp; Entertainment</h2>\r\n                  <p>Enhance your stay with various activities and entertainment options:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li><strong>Jungle Safaris:</strong> Explore the national park\'s diverse wildlife on guided safaris.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Adventure Sports:</strong> Engage in river rafting and other adventure activities for an adrenaline rush.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Local Markets:</strong> Visit nearby markets to buy local handicrafts, souvenirs, and traditional items.</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n            \r\n                  <h2>Getting Around In Jim Corbett</h2>\r\n                  <p>Discover the ease of transportation options in and around Jim Corbett:</p>\r\n                  <ul>\r\n                    <li><strong>Jeep Safaris:</strong> Ideal for wildlife enthusiasts to explore the park\'s diverse terrain.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Taxis:</strong> Convenient for local travel, taxis offer flexibility in exploring nearby areas.</li>\r\n                    <li><strong>Guided Tours:</strong> Opt for guided tours to ensure a seamless and informative experience.</li>\r\n                  </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <a role=\"button\" href=\"#\" class=\"js-show-more float-end\">Show more</a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </section>','<section class=\"card-section\">\r\n      <div class=\"container mt-2\">\r\n        <div class=\"packageheaders\">\r\n        <h3>Best Sellers at Epic Discounts!</h3>\r\n        <p>The Dhikala lodges comprise old and new building structures</p>              \r\n      </div>\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\r\n        <div class=\"custom-card\">\r\n          <img src=\"/newAssets/img/Bijrani-Zone.jpg\" alt=\"Image 1\">\r\n          <div class=\"package-badge\">3D/2N</div> \r\n          <div class=\"card-content\">\r\n            <h6 class=\"lodgetitle\">Corbett Dhikala Forest (1 Night / 2 Days) with 2 Time Jeep Safari </h6>\r\n            <div class=\"rating-and-price\">\r\n              <div class=\"rating\">\r\n                <span class=\"star-icon\">★</span>\r\n                <span class=\"star-icon\">★</span>\r\n                <span class=\"star-icon\">★</span>\r\n                <span class=\"star-icon\">★</span>\r\n                <span class=\"star-icon\">☆</span>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"price\">\r\n                <h4><sup>₹</sup>3500</h4>\r\n              </div>\r\n             \r\n            </div>\r\n            <ul class=\"features\">\r\n              <