      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!-- End Services Section -->','<!-- ======= Services Section ======= -->\r\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"services\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n          <h2>FESTIVAL AND CELEBRATION AT KANKAI</h2>\r\n          <div>\r\n            <p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 20px\">\r\n              If you\'re planning to visit Kankai Mata Temple then you should\r\n              visit during festivals as it\'s a whole different vibe. One of\r\n              the prominent festivals is Navaratri, a nine-night festival all\r\n              about honoring Goddess Durga. This one is most biggest because\r\n              Kankai Mata is seen as a form of Goddess Durga herself. During\r\n              this festival, locals are engaged in beating drums and singing\r\n              devotional songs. Plus, you\'ll see everyone wearing traditional\r\n              clothes in all sorts of vibrant colors, making the whole place\r\n              feel like a party of joyful devotion. It\'s an experience you\r\n              don\'t wanna miss.\r\n            </p>\r\n            <br>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n    <!-- End Services Section -->','<p><br></p>','<p><br></p>','<p><br></p>','<p><br></p>','<p><br></p>','<p><br></p>','2024-03-04 11:24:09','2024-03-16 02:37:05'),(25,'girnar','Gir Girnar Safari Page','Gir Girnar Safari Page','girnar_leafbg2.png','Gir Girnar Safari Page','Gir Girnar Safari Page','testing','testing','<div class=\"col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n            <div class=\"content\">\r\n              <!-- <h3>Tarrif</h3> -->\r\n              <table class=\"table-bordered\">\r\n                <thead class=\"\">\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <th colspan=\"2\" class=\"py-3 px-6 text-center\">\r\n                      Girnar Nature Safari Booking -Tariff\r\n                    </th>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                  <tr class=\"bg-white\">\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">Safari Zones</td>\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">\r\n                      Girnar Nature Safari (Maximum 6 Adults and 1 Child are\r\n                      allowed in 1 Jeep)\r\n                    </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">Price (Indian)</td>\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">\r\n                      Prices may vary, Between 4300 to 6500 (Inclusive of\r\n                      Permit, Gypsy &amp; Guide Charges, Services &amp; Taxes)\r\n                      Depends on Weekends, Number of Persons, Festivals, Long\r\n                      Weekends\r\n                    </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr class=\"bg-white\">\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">Price (Foreigner)</td>\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">\r\n                      Prices may vary, Between 15500 to 17500 (Inclusive of\r\n                      Permit, Gypsy &amp; Guide Charges, Services &amp; Taxes)\r\n                      Depends on Weekends, Number of Persons, Festivals, Long\r\n                      Weekends\r\n                    </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">Note</td>\r\n                    <td class=\"py-3 px-6\">\r\n                      The Payment does not guarantee booking confirmation.\r\n                      Booking would be available only as per seat\r\n                      availability. After payment, visitors will have to call\r\n                      us to confirm their booking. If the booking is not\r\n                      available, your booking will be rescheduled for another\r\n                      date and time with your consent or will be refunded.\r\n                    </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n              </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>','<section id=\"constructions\" class=\"constructions\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n          <h2>Girnar Nature Safari\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>\r\n            Girnar Nature Safari takes place in Girnar Sanctuary. All other parks may have zones for safari or have different routes but there is nothing like that in Girnar Safari, only 1 route has been made for this safari. The safari will start from Indreshwar Naka and will take you 13 km inside the jungle till Paturan beats and then return on the same route. Book your ride quickly because only 8 are allowed each day. The government has only allowed 4 rides in the morning and 4 in the evening. 6 people with 1 kid can go on a safari, the kid should be between 3 to 12 years old. You can spot different kinds of animals during your safari like lions, leopards, deer, crocs, and a bunch more. You can also spot various kinds of birds here. Going on this safari ride is a great way to learn about the flora and fauna because you can ask the guides about the same. \r\n    \r\n          </p>\r\n          <p>Take note that this safari ride remains closed during Girnar Parikrama and Shivratri fair because many pilgrims visit Junagadh during these two festivals.\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>','<section id=\"constructions\" class=\"constructions\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n          <h2>Let’s Know About Girnar Sanctuary\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>\r\n            Girnar Sanctuary is a famous place in Gujarat, India. This place is home to many different kinds of plants and animals. It officially became a wildlife spot in 2008 and the safaris are started here in 2021. These safaris are started to ease the crowd at Gir National Park. Apart from being a pilgrimage spot, this area is home to loads of animals like lions, leopards, deer, crocs, jackals, hyenas, and tons of birds. You can see a lot of wild animals in their natural habitat if you book Girnar Safari. \r\n\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>','<!-- ======= Constructions Section ======= -->\r\n<section id=\"constructions\" class=\"constructions\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n    <h2>GIRNAR HILLS</h2>\r\n    <p>\r\n      Girnar Hills is an awesome place in Junagadh district of Gujarat. They are mountains which are a mix of nature and religion. You can find many historical monuments in this area. Girnar Hills shows off India\'s awesome mix of culture and nature. These hills attract large numbers of Hindus and Jains from all over the world. It’s a famous pilgrimage site which is tough but refreshing at the same time. This place has different topographies, from dense forests to rocky slopes. It’s a treat for nature lovers who enjoy the beautiful views from the mountains. Not just a pilgrimage site, you can visit to famous Girnar Sanctuary near these hills that offer safari rides during which you can spot many wild animals. \r\n    </p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- End Constructions Section -->','<!-- ======= Features Section ======= -->\r\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features section-bg\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <h3>SAFARI TIME\r\n        </h3>\r\n        <p>\r\n          During summer, that is from 1st March to 15th June, the timings of the safari are from 6:00 AM to 9:00 AM and 4 PM to 7 PM\r\n         \r\n        </p>\r\n        <p> During winter, that is from 16th October To 28th/29th February, the timings of safaris are from 6:45 AM to 9:45 AM and 3 PM to 6 PM\r\n        </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n    <!-- End Features Section -->','<!-- ======= Services Section ======= -->\r\n    <div id=\"pilgrimage\" class=\"pilgrimage\">\r\n      <div class=\"container my-4\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n          <h2>Pilgrimage of Girnar\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>People come here for pilgrimage from various parts of the country. Girnar Hills are filled with many Hindu and Jain temples. The pilgrimage to Girnar is not just a physical journey but also a spiritual journey.\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n          <div class=\"constrain-md\">\r\n            <div class=\"card-4\">\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <h4 class=\"text-center\"> Hindu Pilgrims</h4> \r\n                  <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\r\n                    <li class=\"mb-2\">Amba Mata Temple: This is a famous Hindu Temple that is devoted to Goddess Amba. This temple is very famous among Hindus for pilgrimage. Hindus believe that if they take the blessing of Amba Mata then their all wishes will come true. </li>\r\n                    <li>Kalika Mata Temple: As its name says, this temple is devoted to Goddess Kalika. This is a famous pilgrimage site among Hindus. They believe that if they visit this temple then Mata Kalika will bless them. The surroundings of this temple are also very spiritual. \r\n                    </li> \r\n                  </ul> \r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n            <div class=\"card-4\">\r\n              <div class=\"\">\r\n                <h4 class=\"text-center\">Jain Pilgrims</h4>   \r\n                  <ul class=\"bullet-list m-b-4\">\r\n                    <li class=\"mb-2\">Neminath Temple: This temple is a famous pilgrimage site of Jains. This one is dedicated to Lord Neminath. He was famous as the 22nd Tirthankara in Jain Dharm. Pilgrims come here to take blessings.  \r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>Parshwanath Temple: As the name says, this famous Jain temple is dedicated to Lord Parshwanath. He is also the 23rd Tirthankara. The people who follow Jain Dharm believe that visiting this temple will bring blessing and harmony. \r\n                    </li> \r\n                  </ul> \r\n                \r\n              </div>\r\n             \r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    <!-- End Services Section -->','<section id=\"constructions\" class=\"\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n          <h2>Religious Festivals\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>\r\n            Girnar Hills is a must-visit destination during the festival season, especially during Navratri. It attracts pilgrims in large numbers during the festival season. This place is filled with Hindu and Jain pilgrimage temples and because of this reason, this place gets charged with devotion and happiness during festivals. \r\n          </p>\r\n        \r\n      </div>\r\n    </div></section>','<section id=\"constructions\" class=\"\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n        <div class=\"section-header\">\r\n          <h2>Historical Marvels\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>\r\n            Girnar hills are filled with many old Hindu and Jain temples. Not only these temples but there is a 16th-century Jama Masjid also that can be found here. This place also has several historical monuments such as the Uparkot Fort, which dates back to the Mauryan period, along with Ashoka’s rock edicts dating back to the 3rd century BCE. \r\n          </p>         \r\n      </div>\r\n    </div></section>','<!-- ======= Features Section ======= -->\r\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features section-bg\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <h3>Best Time to Visit Girnar Hills </h3>\r\n        <p>\r\n          You can go to Girnar at any time of the year but the best time is from October to March, during this time many festivals are celebrated